<template>
  <v-app>

    <v-app-bar app color="#1F7087">
      <v-app-bar-title class="text-white font-weight-black">管理后台登入</v-app-bar-title>
    </v-app-bar>

    <v-main>

      <v-container fluid>
        <v-row justify="space-around">
          <v-card width="400">
            <v-img
                height="200"
                src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/07/12/07/47/bee-5396362_1280.jpg"
                cover
                class="text-white"
            >
            </v-img>
            <v-card-text>
              <v-text-field
                  v-model="username"
                  label="用户名"
                  required
              ></v-text-field>
              <v-text-field
                  v-model="password"
                  label="用户名"
                  required
              ></v-text-field>
            </v-card-text>
          </v-card>
        </v-row>
      </v-container>

    </v-main>

    <v-footer app>

    </v-footer>

  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "adminLogin"
}
</script>

</style>
